{"tid":48651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角街頭毆鬥3少女    3休班警被捕","createTime":"2016-12-21T07:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T01:41:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2e513a4ddd0f5b57c698a081fcf9bb2e73a58f","tid":48651,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161221/large/1482306369_11d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161221%2Flarge%2F1482306369_11d2.jpg&h=bde84b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3名休班警涉嫌酒後在街頭與3名少女毆鬥，事後全部人被捕。事發於凌晨3時半左右，3名由31-40歲的休班警員，在旺角夜店消遣後帶醉離開，至旺角道28號對開，疑與3名同為22歲的少女踫撞後，一名少女感覺被人觸摸臀部，大怒與3警爭執，雙方繼而大打出手，眾人均手部受傷。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌在公眾地方打架將6人拘捕，全部人事後被送廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，3名被捕休班警員為毒品調查科探員，其中一人為警長。案件交由旺角警區重案組跟進。警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"90e264ee904ab3fabd92309d61dc58506a29b87b","tid":48651,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"打𡃁妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa49fa37c126fda10c19d9d1747936adce0c6fc0","tid":48651,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"休班警+1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01dc6d4641b129d5560e238b02198207dd359c3","tid":48651,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\